    Gender, Race, and Ethnicity Representation Among Gastroenterologists: A Review of Recent Trends.
Despite the urgency of this topic, there is a paucity of data examining trends in gender and racial/ethnic diversity among medical professionals within the field of GI. In this narrative review, we examine how ethnoracial and gender representation has changed over time at critical points along the educational, training, and career pathways in GI.
